comments: She reads every lecture slide word for word and then talks about her personal life in between. It\'s a shame that attendance is taken because I did not benefit from attending. Either she will not even look at your assignment and just give you 100% or she will grade it very very hard, depending on how she feels about you. Stay on her good side.

comments: I took it online and you could do all readings, quizzes, and assignments wayyy ahead of time. The final was the only thing that had to be in a certain time frame. Only half a semester. She was quick with feedback and grading. DO THE READINGS. The quizzes are timed and you only get one try.
